    <entry>
      <title>Cpp_unit06</title>
      <link href="/2024/11/04/Cpp-unit06/"/>
      <url>/2024/11/04/Cpp-unit06/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="const-的引用"><a href="#const-的引用" class="headerlink" title="const 的引用"></a>const 的引用</h2><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">int</span> ci = <span class="number">1024</span>;  <span class="comment">// 明显正确</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">int</span> &amp;r1 = ci;   <span class="comment">// 引用极其对应的对象都是常量</span></span><br><span class="line">r1 = <span class="number">42</span>;   <span class="comment">//错误，r1是对常量的引用</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> &amp;r2 = ci;  <span class="comment">//错误，试图让一个非常量引用指向一个常量对象。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//  常量引用可以指向非常量，反之则是错误的。</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="初始化和对ocnst的引用"><a href="#初始化和对ocnst的引用" class="headerlink" title="初始化和对ocnst的引用"></a>初始化和对ocnst的引用</h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">42</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">int</span> &amp;r1 = i;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">int</span> &amp;r2 = r1 * <span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> &amp;r4 = r1 * <span class="number">2</span>;   <span class="comment">//只有这个是错误的，非常量引用不能指向常量。</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="对const的引用可能引用一个并非const的对象"><a href="#对const的引用可能引用一个并非const的对象" class="headerlink" title="对const的引用可能引用一个并非const的对象"></a>对const的引用可能引用一个并非const的对象</h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">42</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> &amp;r1 = i;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">int</span> &amp;r2 = i;  <span class="comment">//r2也绑定对象i，但是不允许通过r2修改i的值。</span></span><br><span class="line">r1 = <span class="number">0</span>;   <span class="comment">// </span></span><br><span class="line">r2 = <span class="number">0</span>;   <span class="comment">//可以通过*r2来修改i的值</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="指针和const"><a href="#指针和const" class="headerlink" title="指针和const"></a>指针和const</h2><p>指向常量的指针不能用于改变其所指的对象的值。要想存放常量对象的地址，只能使用指向常量的指针。</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">double</span> pi = <span class="number">3.14</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">double</span> *ptr = &amp;pi;   <span class="comment">//ptr是一个普通指针</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">double</span> *cptr = &amp;pi;  <span class="comment">//cptr可以指向一个双精度常量</span></span><br><span class="line">*cptr = <span class="number">42</span>;  <span class="comment">//不能给*cptr赋值</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">double</span> dval = <span class="number">3.14</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cptr = &amp;dval;   <span class="comment">// 正确，但是不能通过cptr改变val的值</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>const 指针</p><p>常量指针必须初始化，初始化完成，则它的值就不能改变。把*放在const关键字之前用以说明指针是一个常量，这样的书写形式隐含着一层意味，即不变的是指针本身的值而非指向的那个值。</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> errNumb = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> *<span class="type">const</span> curErr = &amp;errNumb;  <span class="comment">//curErr将一直指向errNumb</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">double</span> pi = <span class="number">3.14159</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">double</span> *<span class="type">const</span> pip = &amp;pi;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>！！！重要区别</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">const double *ptr = &amp;pi;</span><br><span class="line">定义了一个double 类型的常量指针 ptr。但不能通过ptr修改它所指向的double值。</span><br><span class="line">const double 表示指针指向的值是常量，因此可以改变ptr的指向，但不能通过ptr修改它指向的值</span><br><span class="line">----------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line">double *cosnt ptr = &amp;pi;</span><br><span class="line">这里定义了一个指向指向 double 的常量指针的指针 ptr。</span><br><span class="line">double *const 表示指针本身是常量，不能修改它的指向。  ptr本身的地址是固定的，但是它指向的double类型的指针可以改变，从而允许修改指向double值。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">总结：</span><br><span class="line">const double *ptr：可以改变 ptr 指向的地址，但不能通过 ptr 修改它指向的 double 值。</span><br><span class="line">double *const *ptr：ptr 的地址是固定的，但可以修改 ptr 指向的 double 指针，进而可以通过该指针修改其指向的 double 值。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="顶层const、底层const"><a href="#顶层const、底层const" class="headerlink" title="顶层const、底层const"></a>顶层const、底层const</h3><p>贴一段英文：As we’ve seen, a pointer is an object that can point to a different object. As a result,</p><p>we can talk independently about whether a pointer is const and whether the objects</p><p>to which it can point are const. We use the term <strong>top-level const</strong> to indicate that the</p><p>pointer itself is a const. When a pointer can point to a const object, we refer to</p><p>that const as a <strong>low-level const</strong>.</p><p>top-level const 表示指针本身是个常量，low-level const 表示指针所指的对象是一个常量。</p><p>举几个例子</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> *<span class="type">const</span> p1 = &amp;i;  <span class="comment">// 不能改变p1的值，这是一个顶层const   </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">int</span> ci = <span class="number">42</span>;   <span class="comment">//不能改变ci的值，这是一个顶层const</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">int</span> *p2 = &amp;ci; <span class="comment">// 允许改变p2的值，这是一个底层const</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">int</span> *<span class="type">const</span> p3 = p2;  <span class="comment">//靠右的 const 是顶层 const，靠做的是底层const</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">int</span> &amp;r = ci;  <span class="comment">//用于声明引用的 const 都是底层 const</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>声明的时候：const int 和 int const 是等价的 。声明指向常量的指针是底层const</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> num = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="type">const</span> *p = &amp;num;  <span class="comment">//底层const</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//*p = 2;  指向常量的指针不能改所指的对象</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> num_b = <span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> *<span class="type">const</span> p_b = &amp;num_b;  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// p_b = &amp;num_a;     常量指针不能改变存储地址值</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>来一个助记：如果 const 右结合修饰为 类型 或者 * ，那这个 const 就是一个底层 const； 如果const 右结合修饰为标识符，那这个const 就是一个顶层 const。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">const int ci = 42;</span><br><span class="line">int i = ci;</span><br><span class="line">int * const p = &amp;i;</span><br><span class="line">*p = 0;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>代码解析：ci是const，这个值不能修改； p是常量指针，指向整数类型的变量i。由于指针是const，所以p本身的值（即指向的地址）不能被修改，但可以通过p修改其指向的值。</p><p>*p &#x3D; 0  可以通过指针p修改i的值，将其设置为0     但是不能修改p指向的地址</p><p>多实践就知道顶层或者底层了</p>]]></content>
      
      
